{"tid":1221412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老鼠芬開始縮","createTime":"2019-06-14T07:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T07:59:10.000Z","uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e07222c4df30948af4eea3cde3788ecfeaae6f42","tid":1221412,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:59:10.000Z","msg":"立法會連續三日未能召開大會，但下午安排了內務委員會及財務委員會會議。有建制派議員表示，議會要處理正常事務，有爭議的暫時放一邊。 <br />\n<br />\n立法會連續第三天不開大會，按照議程，下午的內務委員會和財務委員會照開。有建制派議員表示，內會、財會應該開，梁美芬都回到立法會，她指聽到市民意見，不願意見到任何一方受傷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}